          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷饶命啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了然哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我那老和尚呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同锁南枝） 他的年华迈，两鬓黲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年华迈，两鬓黲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了袈裟呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同锁南枝） 金光夺目锦又灿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要谋袈裟是实。故此叫我们放火。害得二位师父呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同锁南枝） 谁料自烧身，送死全无怨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "袈裟放在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那袈裟呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同锁南枝） 藏在观音院，韦陀龛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观音院，韦陀龛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才取去，又不见了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同锁南枝） 伏乞念同衣，饶恕头颅汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饶恕头颅汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说。料你们这些秃厮，也不肯实说。吃老孙一棒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷饶命。我们常闻听老和尚说，这院南有个黑风山，黑风洞，有个黑熊大王。\n想是他见火光起处，被他摄去，也未见得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等说，自然是他摄去了。老和尚既死，与你们无干。去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众僧",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢爷爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众僧同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想起来，都是你这猴头，卖弄我的宝贝，惹出这场祸来。不管。只问你要袈裟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（锁南枝） 你休埋怨，骂再三。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "追取袈裟全在俺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵璧依无憾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那妖怪凶狠，你如何是他的对手？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙悟空 （锁南枝） 任他狰狞貌，恶势憨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狰狞貌，恶势憨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若还说出老孙名，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（锁南枝） 管叫吓破他的胆，吓破他的胆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不管。只问你要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父莫再生嗔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去还须用心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不必再嘱咐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看你这猴孙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧、孙悟空同下。）"
        }
